% Reference:
%   B. Eich and C. Rand Mckinney, "JavaScript Language Specification
%     (Preliminary Draft)", JavaScript 1.1.  1996-11-18.  [Online]
%     http://hepunx.rl.ac.uk/~adye/jsspec11/titlepg2.htm
